Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Ursa Major 大熊座
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}當我大聲喊，你能否聽到？\NCan you hear my voice when I call out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}跟以前比起來，有什麼新的？\NIs there something new from what before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}經歷了這麼多，我能否喘口氣？\NCan I get a break from everything I've gone through?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你也可以看看活了多久\NYou can use that lifetime too
Comment: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}太多雙翅膀，太多匹在飛翔\NWay too many wings, too many up on high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每一雙翅膀，就有隻角\Nand for every pair, there's a horn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}魔法大家有\NMagic's got to spare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感覺能做的還有好多\NFeel like I could be so much more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2500)}就做什麼\NDo anything
Comment: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿能夠—\NFeel like I could--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,—打倒一隻大熊座\N--take down an Ursa Major
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,能抬起這個該死世界\Nlike I could lift up the whole damn world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能否就停止作夢\NBut can I get a break from dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他媽對一個女孩還是太多\Nit's just too much for one damn girl
Comment: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}歷史是給那些不好好玩的人來寫\NHistory is written by the ones who don't play nice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}守規矩的人不會有什麼聲望\NNo fame is gained in behaving
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要是能達成目的我也會開始動亂\NI'd start a riot if it meant I'd get my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聽聽看在那新暑期中的魔力\NListen for the magic in the new type summer phase
